n- Assistant: HEARTBEAT_OK\n\n<read-files>\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-24.md\n</read-files>\n\n<workspace-critical-rules>\n## Every Session\n\nBefore doing anything else:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — this is who you are\n2. Read `USER.md` — this is who you're helping\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nDon't ask permission. Just do it.\n\n## Safety\n\n- Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\n- Don't run destructive commands without asking.\n- `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\n- When in doubt, ask.\n</workspace-critical-rules>","firstKeptEntryId":"addda307","tokensBefore":32033,"details":{"readFiles":["/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md","/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md","/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md","/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-24.md"],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":true}
