{"type":"message","id":"a590366f","parentId":"b5a347f5","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:35:32.484Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我找到问题了！配置中的 webhook URL 好像写错了：\n\n```\nwebhook: \"https://oapi.dingtalk.com/robot/send?access_token=xxx\"\n```\n\n当前配置中，`access_token=` **后面直接跟了注释** `# access token from robot webhook`，这导致实际传给钉钉的 access_token 就是 `xxx# access token from robot webhook`，显然是错的。\n\n同时真正的 access_token 值还是占位符 `xxx`，并没有填入真实的令牌。\n\n让我查看完整的配置文件结构：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2e2kapq8anoh2z2nml75bje7","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.schema.lookup","path":"plugins.entries.dingtalk-connector"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":20176,"output":180,"cacheRead":7480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27836,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774373727762}}
