{"type":"message","id":"5a5e29dd","parentId":"cfe1cfbb","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:35:37.591Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到问题根源了！🔍\n\n**问题分析：**\n1. 钉钉连接器配置中的 `webhook` URL 有误，`access_token` 还是占位符 `xxx`，没有填入真实的 token\n2. 同时注释写法错误，导致整个 URL 被注释污染了\n\n正确的配置应该是：`webhook: \"https://oapi.dingtalk.com/robot/send?access_token=这里放真实的access_token\"`\n\n需要你提供一下钉钉机器人的真实 `access_token`，我来帮你修正配置。你可以在钉钉群机器人设置页面找到 webhook URL，它长这样：\n```\nhttps://oapi.dingtalk.com/robot/send?access_token=abc123def456...\n```\n\n你只需要把 `access_token=` 后面那串真实的 token 发给我就行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":483,"output":187,"cacheRead":27448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28118,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774373734590}}
{"type":"message","id":"1fa57d5d","parentId":"5a5e29dd","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:39:10.586Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-25 01:35:37 GMT+8] [Post-compaction context refresh]\nSystem: \nSystem: Session was just compacted. The conversation summary above is a hint, NOT a substitute for your startup sequence. Run your Session Startup sequence — read the required files before responding to the user.\nSystem: \nSystem: Critical rules from AGENTS.md:\nSystem: \nSystem: ## Every Session\nSystem: \nSystem: Before doing anything else:\nSystem: \nSystem: 1. Read `SOUL.md` — this is who you are\nSystem: 2. Read `USER.md` — this is who you're helping\nSystem: 3. Read `memory/2026-03-25.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\nSystem: 4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\nSystem: \nSystem: Don't ask permission. Just do it.\nSystem: \nSystem: ## Safety\nSystem: \nSystem: - Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\nSystem: - Don't run destructive commands without asking.\nSystem: - `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\nSystem: - When in doubt, ask.\nSystem: \nSystem: Current time: Wednesday, March 25th, 2026 — 1:35 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-24 17:35 UTC\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-03-25 01:39 GMT+8] 是不是应该有clientId，clientSecret就可以了呀，以前还单独给我发送过呢"}],"timestamp":1774373950584}}
