{"type":"message","id":"cfb332e9","parentId":"835e87f0","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:39:23.806Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看到问题了，钉钉连接器有两种模式：\n1. **群机器人 webhook** - 需要 `webhook` （带有 access_token）\n2. **企业内部应用** - 需要 `clientId` + `clientSecret`\n\n你现在配置里两种都混了：\n- webhook 的 URL 写错了，access_token 还是占位符 `xxx`\n- 但是有正确的 clientId/clientSecret\n\n我来修复一下配置，切换到 **企业内部应用模式**：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b78oassjcfpou3tcz5jrhml1","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.patch","path":"plugins.entries.dingtalk-connector.config","raw":"{\n  \"clientId\": \"dingwu1fyvrd4fnxcnnp\",\n  \"clientSecret\": \"EibWwXo8Wl2k1d8NnQcSgFzZJwqfRzYrUaVbWcXdYeZ\",\n  \"webhook\": null\n}","note":"修复钉钉连接器配置，移除错误的 webhook，使用正确的 clientId/clientSecret"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":297,"output":279,"cacheRead":28472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29048,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774373958330}}
