{"type":"message","id":"ef3a8d98","parentId":"c0c638cb","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:48:59.925Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ 发送成功！OpenClaw 返回结果正常，没有报错。\n\n现在麻烦再检查一下钉钉私信，看看能不能收到这条消息：\n\n> 🐉 龙龙仔测试消息！修复了 DM 权限配置，现在应该能收到了吧？😊\n\n刚刚修复了什么问题：\n- 之前 `dmPolicy: \"open\"` 开启了开放私信，但 `allowFrom` 没有配置允许列表\n- 现在添加了 `allowFrom: [\"*\"]`，允许所有人接收/发送消息\n\n如果还是收不到，可能需要确认一下用户 ID `6940612436280423` 是否正确，或者试试发给那个群聊：\n\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_mg64ppaokiykx1gzbh5p1amy","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"dingtalk-connector","target":"chat:6940612436280423","message":"🐉 龙龙仔群聊测试消息！修复了权限配置，如果看到这条消息说明钉钉连接器已经正常工作了 🎉"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":363,"output":270,"cacheRead":30520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31153,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774374535514}}
